      • setEnricher

        public RejectionBus.Builder setEnricher(RejectionEnricher enricher)
        Sets a custom RejectionEnricher for events posted to the RejectionBus which is being built.

        If the RejectionEnricher is not set, the enrichments will NOT be supported for the RejectionBus instance built.

        Parameters:
        enricher - the RejectionEnricher for events or null if enrichment is not supported
